estor magazine in  murren led an extensive reorganization of the company resulting in over  million of annual savings this together with a  billion financing effort kept the company from failure during the early days of the great recession in  and  during murrens tenure mgm joined with dubai world in the development of the las vegas strips citycenter when citycenter opened in december  it represented the largest single private development and the largest green project ever undertaken in the nation’s history and america’s number one generator of new jobs during the great recession senator harry reid said the las vegas community may never be able to express its appreciation adequately for all that jim has done but his hard work hasnt gone unnoticed  he is a leader of his generation in job creation green investment and philanthropy somer hollingsworth president and ceo of the nevada development authority called citycenter the most exciting and impactful project to open for the foreseeable future” under murren’s leadership mgm broke ground on may   on another major project in las vegas a privately financed stateoftheart seat arena that it is developing with sports and entertainment company aeg murren is chair of the american gaming association board of directors the national trade association for the commercial gaming industry and is a member of the board of trustees of the brookings institution in  he was named executive chairman of the board of directors of the corporate responsibility officers association a professional society for corporate responsibility practitioners he was named by president obama to serve on the national infrastructure advisory council he was recognized as executive of the year by casino journal in  during  according to forbes murrens total remuneration from mgm was  million including  million in salary other interestsedit over the years he has been a pioneer in the area of corporate diversity among the companys management ranks more than  percent are minorities and nearly  percent are women during murrens tenure as chairman  ceo the company has continued to garner wide recognition for its leading diversity and inclusion initiatives such as  best companies for diversity black enterprise magazine top  companies for latinos diversityinc magazine best places to work for lgbt equality human rights campaign foundation top  regional companies diversityinc top  companies for mba students universum global and top corporation for women’s business enterprises womens business enterprise national council fortune magazine has named mgm resorts one of the world’s most admired companies corporate responsibility cr magazine a publication which recognizes americas most socially responsible chief executives named murren a  responsible ceo of the year award winner the annual awards are presented to ceos across industries that clearly exceed standards in the areas of employee relations environmental impact human rights philanthropy and corporate responsibility practices in  he was the recipient of the distinguished leader award by the university of massachusetts’ isenberg school of management he founded the nevada cancer institute and actively supports trinity college the johns hopkins university the fisher house foundation for veterans and military families and other nonprofit organizations he currently serves as an executive in residence at johns hopkins universitys carey business school referencesedit  institutional investor feb   and march     james murren  news articles biography photos  people mgm resorts international mgm  james j murren profile  forbes  business wire  pr newswire  las vegas review journal  council for a better nevada  council for a better nevada  snell alan shovels in the ground confetti in the air as mgmaeg arena construction begins the las vegas reviewjournal  anderer charles  december  roaring back casino journal retrieved  january    james murren forbes retrieved  january    austin grace april   d